EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1800Z DAILY
   02 THRU 12 DEC WITHIN 20 MILES OF:
   A. 57-16N 008-05W.
   B. 57-30N 008-31W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 121900Z DEC 13.
